<paragraph role="heading" id="hd_id3160463" xml-lang="en-US" level="1" l10n="U" oldref="1"><link href="text/shared/01/03110000.xhp" name="Full Screen">Full Screen</link></paragraph>
<paragraph role="paragraph" id="par_id3148983" xml-lang="en-US" l10n="CHG" oldref="2"><ahelp hid=".uno:FullScreen">Shows or hides the menus and toolbars in Writer or Calc. To exit the full screen mode, click the <emph>Full Screen On/Off</emph> button.</ahelp></paragraph>
</section>
